Package: europarl
Type: Package
Title: Data Package to Download and Store the Europarl Corpus
Version: 0.0.4
Date: 2019-12-16
Authors@R: person("Andreas Blaette", "Developer", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "andreas.blaette@uni-due.de")
Imports:
  cwbtools (>= 0.1.1),
  curl,
  stringi
Suggests:
  knitr,
  rmarkdown,
LazyData: yes
Description: Minimal functionality to download a subset of the Europarl Corpus, version 3,
  pre-indexed for the IMS Open Corpus Workbench (CWB). It is based on the POS-tagged,
  lemmatised and sentence-aligned distribution offered by the OPUS project
  (<http://urd.let.rug.nl/tiedeman/OPUS/Europarl3.php>) and includes the languages English,
  Dutch, French, German, Italian and Spanish. The six corpora are available under the CWB
  names EUROPARL-EN, EUROPARL-NL, EUROPARL-FR, EUROPARL-DE, EUROPARL-IT and EUROPARL-ES.
